OL,4,CProtesters halt work on Gandhi statue
OL,5, A court in Malawi has halted work on a
OL,6, statue of Mahatma Gandhi after critics
OL,7, accused him of using racial slurs.
OL,9,F"Being black people ourselves, such
OL,10,Fremarks have invited a sense of
OL,11,Floathing and detestation of Gandhi,"
OL,12,Fthe Gandhi Must Fall group said in its
OL,13,Fcourt application.
OL,15,FJudge Michael Tembo granted an
OL,16,Finjunction temporarily suspending work
OL,17,Fon the statue.
OL,19,FThe effigy's construction was part of a
OL,20,F$10m (B#7.8m) building deal with India.
